				</p>
			</div>
			<div>
				<svg class="w-10 h-10 mb-2 text-purple-500 md:w-12 md:h-12 dark:text-purple-500" fill="currentColor"
					viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
					<path
